{"tid":2405092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大：不再轉播BBC 是去除英國殖民地色彩的表現","createTime":"2021-02-12T06:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T17:37:20.000Z","uid":225931,"like":14,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"83a507775bde77d1e84a9d776bc474496c907f47","tid":2405092,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"國家廣播電視總局通報，對英國廣播公司BBC世界新聞台，繼續在中國境內落地的新一年度申請，不予受理。中大新聞與傳播學院講師梁麗娟表示，內地通過衛星接收電視節目的人較以往少，實際影響可能是部分酒店住客，但現時旅遊業已經停頓，因此影響不是很大。<br />\n<br />\n梁麗娟分析，內地電視廣播模式已經走向式微，內地民眾都喜歡在網上獲取資訊，而BBC有透過網上發送服務，一些民眾透過虛擬私人網絡VPN去接收，海外旅客亦可用本身國家或地區的電話卡，上網接收BBC資訊，只不過不能在酒店電視收看BBC新聞，認為中方的行動象徵大於實際。<br />\n<br />\n對於香港電台不再轉播BBC部分節目，梁麗娟認為，這是跟隨內地主旋律的做法，亦是去除英國殖民地色彩的表現。"},{"pid":"9df4ea2c8585e0cb3ba948b2ea2e0e1edc483e06","tid":2405092,"uid":225931,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"中文大學新聞與傳播學院講師梁麗娟<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.com.cuhk.edu.hk/zh-TW/people-m/teaching-staff/leung-grace-l-k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.com.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fzh-TW%2Fpeople-m%2Fteaching-staff%2Fleung-grace-l-k&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FHr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=266aeaef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.com.cuhk.edu.hk/zh-TW/people-m/teaching-staff/leung-grace-l-k</a>"},{"pid":"db6ec77c25f957e09334200c3e157ecb0e76142a","tid":2405092,"uid":301952,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"國防定外交事務 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c87558cf112ececf2144bd31924ce7cdb08750","tid":2405092,"uid":300782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"新聞系講屍 唔聽新聞"},{"pid":"16fcb1eb3fe43741f5a0ab227f3abc76552d1f53","tid":2405092,"uid":155095,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:23:50.000Z","msg":"<del>亦是去除英國殖民地色彩的表現。</del><br />\n<br />\n亦是一國一制色彩的表現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7f4eb77d6a3e36c98f25746600d57ed077910a","tid":2405092,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"標題黨"},{"pid":"b25ce0b2262d67956e201fbcab75863787aa2107","tid":2405092,"uid":21141,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"去除英國殖民地色彩就罷免特區政府<br />\n由中央全面接管啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82922846882f7a3380227b311ca769788725794","tid":2405092,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實無講錯 香港人心回歸一定要去殖"},{"pid":"c5673a159fcd3c6d861e854d181baa2c089dbc30","tid":2405092,"uid":34409,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:36:05.000Z","msg":"香港公務員同大學講師薪酬都充滿殖民地特色"},{"pid":"b2cb7b0960ed41224b7bb4cfaa7d73ed98f0082e","tid":2405092,"uid":157439,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"港交所要唔要太古除牌？"},{"pid":"dc2cd12ee8cbfd5f237edd1a0113e946763da972","tid":2405092,"uid":34409,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:36:53.000Z","msg":"香港公務員同大學講師薪酬都充滿殖民地特色"},{"pid":"f11ab288bff0d4d65db59b58f8ed63e6301c0c68","tid":2405092,"uid":60451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2cb7b0960ed41224b7bb4cfaa7d73ed98f0082e","tid":2405092,"uid":157439,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"港交所要唔要太古除牌？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"係囉<br />\n怡和都應該要收皮"},{"pid":"b939f28b067e75163b46e7d89260777b0b74df74","tid":2405092,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:41:21.000Z","msg":"變中國殖民地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8689036c66454d4e5b5285d943471a2ecb803747","tid":2405092,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim